# Cursor Rules Location Enforcement

<!-- desc: Ensures every .mdc rule file stays inside .cursor/rules/. -->

<rule>
name: cursor_rules_location
description: Reject rule files not placed in .cursor/rules/
filters:
  - type: file_extension
    pattern: "\\.mdc$"
  - type: event
    pattern: "file_create"
actions:
  - type: reject
    conditions:
      - pattern: "^(?!\\.cursor\\/rules\\/).*"
        message: "Cursor rule files (.mdc) must reside in .cursor/rules/. Move the file accordingly."
</rule>

